				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$ RWC=\left(FW\mathit{\hbox{-}}DW/TW\mathit{\hbox{-}}DW\right)*100 $$\end{document}RWC=FW‐DW/TW‐DW*100

Leaf spectral reflectance, at wavelengths from 400 to 1000 nm with an interval of ~0.2 nm, was measured at mid-day using a portable narrow-band width spectrometer (CI-700, CID Bio-Science Inc., USA). Leaf chlorophyll concentration was estimated using transformed chlorophyll absorption in reflectance index (TCARI) [74]:\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
